<div id="mcplawi-start" class="container">
  <div class="row-buffer welcome">
    <p class="club-welcome-text">Welcome from the
      MCPLA of Wisconsin!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-buffer">
    <div class="col-md-6 bottom-buffer">
      <center>
        <%= image_tag 'user-5.png', class: 'main-icons' %>
      </center>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="club-info-text"><b><%= link_to 'CREATE AN ACCOUNT', new_user_registration_path %></b> and register for any event posted by the Milwaukee County Public Links Association! Already a member? You can <b><%= link_to 'LOGIN', new_user_session_path %></b> here. Keep your profile up to date with your email address and home club and membership status!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-buffer">
    <div class="col-md-6 bottom-buffer">
      <center>
        <%= image_tag 'credit-card.png', class: 'main-icons' %>
      </center>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="club-info-text">Register and pay for <b><%= link_to 'EVENTS', events_path %></b> online! Payments are easy as you can pay from the conveinence of your home or mobile phone! You will be emailed a receipt and a confirmation for your event registration.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-buffer">
    <div class="col-md-6 bottom-buffer">
      <center>
        <%= image_tag 'golfer.png', class: 'main-icons' %>
      </center>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="club-info-text">Check back here as the tournament date approaches. Tee-times, results and the winners picture for each flight will be posted on each tournament page! Utilize the <b><%= link_to 'PLAYERS PAGE', players_path %></b> to find and connect with fellow MCPLA golfers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-buffer">
      <div class="col-md-6 bottom-buffer">
        <center>
          <%= image_tag 'newspaper.png', class: 'main-icons' %>
        </center>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p class="club-info-text">Keep up to date with the MCPLAWI! We will periodically post <b><%= link_to 'MEETING MINUTES', minutes_path %></b> as well as new <b><%= link_to 'NEWS AND UPDATES', notes_path %></b> to help keep you informed!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3">
      <br>
      <br>
      <center class="flat-icon"> 
        <p>Icons made by <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/authors/twitter" target="_blank" title="Twitter">Twitter</a> from <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/" target="_blank" title="Flaticon">www.flaticon.com</a><br>Licensed by <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/" 			    title="Creative Commons BY 3.0" target="_blank">CC 3.0 BY</a></p>
      </center>
    </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-offset-2">
    <%= image_tag 'mcplawi.jpg', class: 'img-responsive main-logo' %>
  </div>
</div>